{"tid":610592,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[無知一問］係咪咩政權一統治中原就係中國","createTime":"2018-03-30T06:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T19:15:52.000Z","uid":48609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c910457861b37dfd3bc9be340ba323af77c7ede1","tid":610592,"uid":48609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"元清太遠無得講 <br />\n最近日本贏左的話 係咪叫日朝？<br />\n中原人就不知不覺當左日本係佢地領土？<br />\n變到好似東北三省？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/140217_faa32b9fa73139f85dd4eba1aee31e26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F140217_faa32b9fa73139f85dd4eba1aee31e26.png&h=886f65e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b54803ebedebfbeb924aa06e8096194a7ce078f","tid":610592,"uid":48609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20f223bac72de99812cfd5f94b8bcd58d662ee2e","tid":610592,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"YES"},{"pid":"39fbce4786cefb0b72db283cd7b62cfcee8c6828","tid":610592,"uid":48609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f223bac72de99812cfd5f94b8bcd58d662ee2e","tid":610592,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"YES"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"咁其實好撚無賴 ....同堆南亞人用人口殖民歐洲有咩分別"},{"pid":"6c4ec95df7b1de97053a577ea36488117b1c542e","tid":610592,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"史書成日吹宋後無華夏<br />\n明亡無華夏之類<br />\n查實由五胡亂華開始<br />\n拿，連教科書個ＴＯＰＩＣ都可以概括成五個外族入侵華夏文明就明哂啦<br />\n<br />\n其實華夏呢個ＴＥＲＭ只係一種民族主義意識，洗洗地腦<br />\n真係要講中國史<br />\n要固定返個概念係個個民族邊度起源，架構同擴張係點<br />\n符合哂所謂中國既定義就真係西